'''Jennifer Hale''' ([[30 January|January 30]], [[1972]]) is a Canadian-born American voice actress. She has provided voices for several animated productions of [[Disney]] and Marvel, and various roles in ''Star Wars'' video games. 

==Roles==
* [[2017]]: ''[[Middle-earth: Shadow of War]]'' - [[Galadriel]]
* [[2014]]: ''[[Middle-earth: Shadow of Mordor]]'' - [[Galadriel]]
* [[2011]]: ''[[The Lord of the Rings: War in the North]]'' - Idonna Bellflower
* [[2003]]: [[The Hobbit (2003 video game)|''The Hobbit'' (2003 video game)]] - Lianna, additional voices 
* [[2001]]:  [[The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring (video game)|''The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring'' (video game)]] - [[Galadriel]], [[Lobelia Sackville-Baggins|Lobelia]], [[Rose Cotton]]
